ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectOrder Approving the Boundary Change of the district of the Bragg Creek and Area Chamber of Commerce
PrecisOrder approving the application by the BRAGG CREEK AND AREA CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Alberta, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of its district from Township 23 ranges 3, 4 and 5, and Township 24 range 4 to Townships 22 and 23 inclusive, ranges 3, 4 and 5 and Township 24 range 4, all being west of the Fifth Meridian in Alberta.
